<TEXT>
cincinnatis tom browning pitched the 14th 
perfect game in major league baseballs 108year history breezing 
past the los angeles dodgers 10 friday night 
it also was the first nohitter since the beginning of last 
season six nohit bids were broken up this season including one 
by the reds browning 
