served as a mediator to set up the meeting said some bitter 
things were exchanged during the six hours of talks he did not 
elaborate 
the meeting was to discuss terms for largescale talks on 
polands future including the subject of solidarity and trade 
union pluralism the sides agreed that the talks would convene in 
midoctober 
