take 76 days or about half as long as it took the cherokees to get 
to oklahoma participants are financing the trip out of their own 
pockets except for 1000 donated by the state of illinois he 
said 
i know well run into some problems along the way but they 
wont be anything compared with the sacrifices the cherokees had to 
make he said 
