borrowing here 
the increasing frequency of japanese acquisitions in the united 
states may accelerate that development as japanese companies look 
for new sources of funds to help them finance those purchases he 
said 
now that a major leader among japanese companies has taken 
this initial step other japanese companies will follow suit he 
said 
